---
---

<section class="hero">
	<div class="scanlines" aria-hidden="true"></div>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="eyebrow">
			<span class="dot"></span>
			<span class="eyebrow-text">PICOCLUSTER CLAW // desktop AI datacenter</span>
		</div>

		<div class="beta-strip" role="note">
			<span class="beta-tag">BETA</span>
			<span class="beta-text">
				The stack is moving fast. <strong>OpenClaw</strong>,
				<strong>ThreadWeaver</strong>, and the
				<strong>Ollama model catalog</strong> all ship frequent
				updates. Pin a release if you need stability —
				<code>git pull</code> if you want the edge.
			</span>
		</div>

		<h1>
			A desktop AI datacenter.
			<span class="glow">Yours, on your network.</span>
		</h1>

		<p class="lede">
			PicoCluster Claw is a two-node compute appliance that runs
			<strong class="hl-blue">OpenClaw</strong> — a local automation
			runtime with tool-calling — alongside a dedicated CUDA inference
			node. One private execution surface for the agents and models you
			already use.
		</p>

		<p class="lede">
			<strong class="hl-white">14W</strong> idle.
			<strong class="hl-white">~$2/month</strong> to keep running.
			Boots in seconds, stays up 24/7, and answers on your LAN — no
			API keys, no metered tokens, no traffic off the network.
		</p>

		<div class="cta-row">
			<a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://picocluster.com" rel="noopener">
				Order yours →
			</a>
			<a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/getting-started/quickstart/">
				Read the docs
			</a>
		</div>

		<p class="badges">
			<span class="badge">OpenClaw runtime</span>
			<span class="badge">Dedicated CUDA node</span>
			<span class="badge badge-red">No API keys</span>
			<span class="badge">Always-on</span>
			<span class="badge">Open source</span>
		</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.hero {
		position: relative;
		padding: 6rem 0 4.5rem 0;
		background:
			radial-gradient(
				ellipse 60% 80% at 50% 0%,
				rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.14),
				transparent 60%
			),
			radial-gradient(
				ellipse 50% 40% at 85% 30%,
				rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.08),
				transparent 55%
			),
			var(--ctx-bg);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ctx-border-lo);
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.scanlines {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		pointer-events: none;
		background: repeating-linear-gradient(
			to bottom,
			transparent 0,
			transparent 2px,
			rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.015) 2px,
			rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.015) 3px
		);
		mix-blend-mode: screen;
	}

	.container {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.eyebrow {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.55rem;
		padding: 0.35rem 0.85rem;
		background: rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.1);
		border: 1px solid rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.35);
		border-radius: 999px;
		font-family: var(--ctx-font-mono);
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		color: var(--claw-blue-text);
		margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
	}

	.eyebrow .dot {
		width: 8px;
		height: 8px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: var(--claw-blue);
		box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.8);
		animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	@keyframes pulse {
		0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
		50% { opacity: 0.4; }
	}

	.eyebrow-text {
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.beta-strip {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
		gap: 0.65rem;
		padding: 0.6rem 0.85rem;
		margin: 0 0 1.75rem 0;
		background: rgba(252, 211, 77, 0.06);
		border: 1px solid rgba(252, 211, 77, 0.28);
		border-radius: var(--ctx-radius-md);
		max-width: 44rem;
	}

	.beta-tag {
		flex-shrink: 0;
		padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
		background: rgba(252, 211, 77, 0.15);
		border: 1px solid rgba(252, 211, 77, 0.35);
		border-radius: 999px;
		font-family: var(--ctx-font-mono);
		font-size: 0.65rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		color: var(--ctx-warn);
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1.4;
	}

	.beta-text {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: var(--ctx-text-dim);
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	.beta-text strong {
		color: #ffffff;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.beta-text code {
		font-family: var(--ctx-font-mono);
		font-size: 0.9em;
		color: var(--claw-blue-text);
		background: rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.1);
		border: 1px solid rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.25);
		padding: 0.05rem 0.3rem;
		border-radius: var(--ctx-radius-sm);
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5.5vw, 3.75rem);
		font-weight: 800;
		line-height: 1.05;
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
		color: #ffffff;
		letter-spacing: -0.025em;
		max-width: 18ch;
	}

	h1 .glow {
		color: var(--claw-blue-text);
		text-shadow:
			0 0 30px rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.5),
			0 0 60px rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.25);
	}

	.lede {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--ctx-text-dim);
		margin: 0 0 1.1rem 0;
		max-width: 40rem;
		line-height: 1.65;
	}

	.lede:last-of-type {
		margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
	}

	.hl-blue {
		color: var(--claw-blue-text);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.hl-white {
		color: #ffffff;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.cta-row {
		display: flex;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.badges {
		display: flex;
		gap: 0.6rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.badge {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
		background: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.6);
		border: 1px solid var(--ctx-border);
		border-radius: 999px;
		font-size: 0.72rem;
		color: var(--ctx-text-dim);
		font-family: var(--ctx-font-mono);
		letter-spacing: 0.04em;
	}

	.badge-red {
		border-color: rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.35);
		color: var(--claw-red-text);
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.hero {
			padding: 4rem 0 3rem 0;
		}
	}
</style>
